  33:middlewares/freertos/source/portable/memmang/heap_4.c ****  * memory management pages of https://www.FreeRTOS.org for more information.
  34:middlewares/freertos/source/portable/memmang/heap_4.c ****  */
  35:middlewares/freertos/source/portable/memmang/heap_4.c **** #include <stdlib.h>
  36:middlewares/freertos/source/portable/memmang/heap_4.c **** 
